Titolo: The G.G. Shinobi II: The Silent Fury

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: The G.G. Shinobi II: The Silent Fury (ザ・GG忍 II) is a side-scrolling action game by Sega released for the Game Gear in 1992. It is the sequel to The G.G. Shinobi, an offshoot of the Shinobi series created for Sega's portable platform. The player controls Joe Musashi as he rendezvous with his ninja allies from the previous game, giving the player access to different characters with unique abilities as the game progresses.

Genere: Platformer 

Valutazione: N/A
